These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, cycling, golf
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | golf | cycling | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pepper, cauliflower, grapes
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | pepper | grapes | cauliflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, camping, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | singing | camping | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, soul, ambient
1. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | ambient | soul |

